Feb 18 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Alfen NV, L'Oreal and TUI AG, on Friday.


HIGHLIGHTS

* Airbus Group AIR.PA: Morgan Stanley raises target price to EUR 137 from EUR 135

* Alfa Laval AB ALFA.ST: Exane BNP Paribas starts with outperform rating; SEK 350 PT

* Alfen NV ALFEN.AS: Berenberg raises to buy from hold

* L'Oreal OREP.PA: Barclays raises to overweight from underweight

* TUI AG TUIT.L: HSBC raises target price to 300p from 260p
